					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Suggested layout for your PRG:
<br />16 KB bank 0: bankswitched stuff.
<br />16 KB bank 1: bankswitched stuff.
<br />16 KB bank 2: instructions on how to build an atomic bomb.
<br />16 KB bank 3: hardwired stuff.
<br />
<br />Just stick a random text file in there as an easter egg; that's what was done for The New Tetris on N64.</div>

